        "generateUrl": "https://my.g2.com/developers",
        "setup": "Create or log into your organization in the [G2 Developer Portal](https://my.g2.com/developers). To mint a token, open the **Access Tokens** tab, choose **Generate Token**, name the token, choose a **Resource Owner** (`User` or `Organization`), assign endpoint permissions, and save. The portal reveals the token once; copy it and store it securely. G2's docs say you can then use it against the [G2 API reference](https://data.g2.com/api/v2/docs/index.html)."
